{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"到处唱起丰收歌——河南新民歌选","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":6,"day":10}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处唱起丰收歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——河南新民歌选"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向毛主席报喜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小白鸽，你别停，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带个喜讯到北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"见了毛主席先问好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再报喜讯给他听："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“今年麦子长得好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亩打千斤有保证。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（登封　吴金海）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦子长得轩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出村去，到西弯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"块块麦子长得轩，〔注〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肥头大脑真好看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人要进去埋住肩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东头推着西头动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六寸麦穗沉甸甸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（登封　玿献）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔注〕轩是好的意思。没见过这样的好庄稼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梁大爷，七十八，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耳不聋，眼不花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨晚东洴去开会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"见了社长笑哈哈："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“咱社麦子今年好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每亩能打五百八，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的年纪这么大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没见过这样的好庄稼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这全凭党的好领导，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全凭社员干劲大。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰产粮多多送工厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支援社会主义工业化。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（登封　冯银富）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰收有保障"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃进声中凯歌响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"右倾保守一扫光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干部群众齐努力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土地潜力齐解放。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦高长到五尺半，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穗大籽饱四寸长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹麦子起金浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年丰收有保障。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（安阳　灯塔农业社）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处唱起丰收歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石榴开花红似火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万顷麦浪翻金波，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年是个好收成，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男女社员忙收割。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收割机，马拉着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶马的人儿机上坐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长杆鞭儿空中响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海龙白马拉的泼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辛勤一天回家转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处唱起丰收歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（登封　赵改名）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颗粒还家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏收如打仗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏种破上命。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颗粒全还家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掉粒如掉命。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（偃师　杨裴屯社）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手争得粮满仓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕烈日晒破皮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕地热脚烙烂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手争得粮满仓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血汗培育稻苗田。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（偃师　翟镇社）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河南民歌整理组“奔流”编辑部搜集整理"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}